# MCP routing (summary)

Development is **100% in Cursor**. **Scripts first** — MCPs augment, never replace gates.

Invoke MCP tools with **`CallMcpTool`** (read each tool's JSON descriptor first). Use **Shell** for terminal commands.

Configured in **`~/.cursor/mcp.json`** (not committed). Peekaboo and mirroir launch via
`$HOME/.cursor/bin/mcp_stdio_wrapper.sh`.

## Server quick-ref

| Server | Use for |
| --- | --- |
| `user-xcodebuildmcp` | macOS quick build/test; `ios-device` profile helper only — **`scripts/*.sh` primary** |
| `user-context7` | Non-Apple library docs (`resolve-library-id` → `query-docs`) |
| `user-axiom` | Apple skills, auditors, `axiom_xcsym_*` / `axiom_xcprof_*` / `axiom_xclog_*` |
| `mirroir` | iOS exploratory QA only → [agent-ui-driving.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/agent-ui-driving.mdc) |
| `peekaboo` | macOS exploratory QA only |
| `plugin-chrome-devtools-mcp-chrome-devtools` / `cursor-ide-browser` | `website/` verification |
| `plugin-huggingface-skills-huggingface-skills` | Hub model/dataset lookup |
| `cursor-app-control` | IDE control (sparingly) |

**mirroir setup:** `scripts/install_mirroir_user_config.sh` + Cursor restart; preflight
`scripts/ios_mirroir_preflight.sh`. French macOS: `~/.mirroir-mcp/settings.json` →
`mirroringProcessName: "Recopie de l'iPhone"`. Driving: [ios-agent-ui-tour.md](mdc:docs/reference/ios-agent-ui-tour.md) Appendix **B.5–B.8**.

## Hard routing

- **iOS:** never Simulator / sim MCP / Axiom `xcui` — [`AGENTS.md`](mdc:AGENTS.md) Hard rules
- **Gates:** `macos_test.sh gate` / `ios_device.sh gate` — never agent-driven screen control
- **xcodebuildmcp:** call `session_show_defaults` before first build/run/test in a session

